question: Where can I find restaurant heading towards Beltzville State Park - Preacher's Camp Boat Launch, Lehighton, PA from Gemberling-Rex House, Schaefferstown, PA, within a radius of 120 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.293232 40.29829)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.574758 40.874297)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.293232 40.29829)',4326)::geography, 120000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.293232 40.29829)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
